The mainwindow carrys as title the name of the current project. It has a statusbar,
in which a little help is shown, when the pointer is over a gadget.
There are also filing-cards, which contents a determined systemcomponent.
So there are 13 different pages:

            @{"Screen-page         " link Mainwinscreens}
            @{"Window-page         " link Mainwinwindows}
